  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BuildingLevel, Home, HomeArea, StairCase, StairWay

    public abstract class IndoorPlace
extends Place
    Ontological representation of a place that is covered (indoors). Methods included in this class are the mandatory ones for representing an ontological concept in Java classes for universAAL. Usually it includes getters and setters for most of its properties.
    Author:
    chwirth
